# @baseUrl = http://localhost:8787
# @baseUrl = https://message-api.<your-subdomain>.workers.dev
@baseUrl = https://message-api.dhairyashah98.workers.dev

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Log read receipt (returns {})
GET {{baseUrl}}/read

### List read receipts — defaults: page=1, limit=20
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-receipts

### List read receipts — paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-receipts?page=1&limit=5
 
### Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-receipts?page=2&limit=1
